APIs ( I used the POST method with all of the APIS ):

1) Login (Method: POST)
   - URL: http://homestead.test/api/login
   - input email, password
   
2) Me (Method: POST):
   - URL: http://homestead.test/api/me
   - input: token

3) refresh token (Method: POST)
   - URL: http://homestead.test/api/refresh
   - input: token

4) Logout (Method: POST):
  - URL: http://homestead.test/api/logout
  - input: token

5) get All Cities (Method: POST)
  - URL: http://homestead.test/api/cities
   - input: token

6) Add a city (Method: POST):
   - URL: http://homestead.test/api/cities/create
   - input: token , name_en , image_uri
   
7) show city (Method: POST):
   - URL: http://homestead.test/api/cities/{id}
   - input: token
  
8) Update a city (Method: POST)
  - URL: http://homestead.test/api/cities/update/{id}
  - input: token , name_en , Image_uri

9) Delete a city (Method: POST)
   - URL: http://homestead.test/api/delete/{id}
   - input: token 

10) Get city places (Method: POST)
   - URL: http://homestead.test/api/cities/places/{id}
   - input: token

11) get All places (Method: POST)
   - URL: http://homestead.test/api/places
   - input: token

12) Add a place (Method: POST)
   - URL: http://homestead.test/api/places/create
   - input: token , name_en , description, long , lat , image_uri , city_id , category_id
      
13) show place (Method: POST):
   - URL: http://homestead.test/api/places/{id}
   - input: token
  

13) Update a place (Method: POST)
    - URL: http://homestead.test/api/places/update/{id}
   - input: token , name_en , description, long , lat , image_uri , city_id , category_id


14) Delete a place (Method: POST)
    - URL: http://homestead.test/api/places/delete/{id}
   - input: token

15) Find a place by name (Method: POST)
    - URL: http://homestead.test/api/places/search
   - input: token , keyword

16) Get User Favorite places (Method: POST)
  - URL: http://homestead.test/api/userPlaces
  - input: token 

17) Add a place to favorite (Method: POST)
   - URL: http://homestead.test/api/userPlaces/add
   - input: token , place_id
   
18) Remove a place form favorite (Method: POST)
   - URL: http://homestead.test/api/userPlaces/delete
   - input: token , place_id
   
 
 
